# Document Parsing Prompts

Reference these prompts using: `@prompt-library/document-parsing prompt-name`

## Fix Spaces Between Letters

**Use when:** Text has spaces between letters that should be removed (anagram fix)

```
this has sentences and words but some of them have spaces in between the letters, making it not complete sentences or words. it is an anagram that should make complete sentences and words.
```

## Fix Paragraph Newlines

**Use when:** Paragraphs have extra newlines in the middle

```
the text has paragraphs in it but they have extra new lines in the middle of the sentences that make up the paragraph. i only want new lines to be at the beginning and end of the paragraphs. can you fix this?
```
